data.description: Living in this charming country-style home in Marsing, situated by the Sunnyslope Wine Trail, offers a unique blend of tranquility and natural beauty. Enjoy distinctive features such as no rear neighbors, views of Lizard Butte, a cozy fireplace and a 3-car garage where you can make the most of the extra space. in addition to parking your vehicles, you could create a workshop area, a home gym, or even a storage space for outdoor equipment like bicycles, kayaks, or gardening tools. All of this gives you a wonderful canvas to create your ideal lifestyle. So many opportunities to maximize your enjoyment of this lovely property. Repairs to be completed in a couple of weeks. All new flooring to be placed in the kitchen and front room. Pick your flooring if you hurry!
